    "title": "Manufacturing Engineer - Charak Pharma - Top MNC",
    "description": "Charak Pharma has an exciting opening for a Manufacturing Engineer at our Gurgaon office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Charak Pharma:\nCharak Pharma is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Charak Pharma!",
